Hi! We’re the Showalters! 

I don’t typically share my family a lot on here but they are a huge part of me so I thought I’d take a minute to share a little bit about our family💕

-We moved to Las Vegas 6 years ago from Colorado🎲 It was such a culture shock at first but now we love it and it feel like home. (At least for now😉)

-I was a hairstylist before having kids and now social media is my full time job! Tyler has worked  in the airlines as long as I’ve known him and funny enough, I come from an airline family so it just felt right! We both have unconventional jobs but it works for us and we both feel really lucky to actually love what we do! 

-Tyler is the cook in our family and he’s a little too good at it.😋
And I cook…..Trader Joe’s meals👩🏼‍🍳 

-We don’t have typical gender roles in our family. We’re truly equal partners in life and are raising our girls to know that’s the norm💪🏼 

-Our girls are just two months shy of 4 years apart and I know I’m bias but I think it’s the PERFECT age difference. They’re best friends! 

I love these three so much and although I don’t believe my entire purpose in life is to be a wife and mother I sure am glad it’s apart of this life I’m living🥰
